      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped free range chicken </strong>to the pan and cook for 2 min</p><p>Stir in your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and add your <strong>tomato paste</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle of oil if the pan looks a little dry</p>",
